column5: Anyone know if Wolseley Bay on the French is opened up yet?  Heading up for a week on the 16th.

http://coastwatch.glerl.noaa.gov/modis/modis.php?region=h&page=2&template=sub&image=t1.15109.1555.LakeHuron.143.250m.jpg  main channel with current has been open for a while, some slack water is still frozen
